data.description: South Shore Tampa Bay. Lovely 4 bedroom 2 bath home located in highly desired Mira Lago gated community in suburb of Tampa Bay. Interior features include large open floor plan with 9-foot ceilings. Dining room and large living room with amazing view of backyard. Spacious kitchen has stainless steel appliances, island with additional cabinets for storage, Corian countertops cabinets, walk-in pantry and counter that overlooks the family room. Spacious Master suite with walk-in closet, Master bath with double vanities, huge tub and separate shower. Ceiling fans in bedrooms and family room. Flooring includes ceramic tile and laminate. Inside laundry room, Glass sliders to the amazingly peaceful backyard overlooking small lake. Backyard is picturesque with peaceful view. Perfect for grilling and family gatherings with water view and no backdoor neighbors. 3-minute drive to community pool, basketball court, playground. Located just minutes from Bahia beach at Little Harbor Marina and pier. Schedule appointment today to view this fabulous home.
